                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>2004-06-25</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>I picked up this book on the way home from a trip for some airplane reading and could not put it down. I was somewhat familiar with Jenifer's story from seeing her and her sisters on the Today Show and other news programs when they started Project ALS. But her courageous story of life and love and what it means to be family really touched my heart - and gave me some much needed perspective in my life. I highly recommend it!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Indomitable spirit an encouragement to all</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
